Data Analysis of UpX Whatsapp Group 'UpX Team'¶

To read complete blog please visit my homepage

Reading file & pre-processing¶

In [1]:
import pandas as pd
In [2]:
f = 'UpX.txt'
In [3]:
list_ = []
with open(f,encoding="utf8") as mg:
    for line in mg:
        try:
            if(type(int(line[0:2])) == int and line.count(':') == 2):
               list_.append (line)
        except:
            pass
In [4]:
import re

mg = pd.DataFrame([re.split(', | - |: ',sub) for sub in list_])
In [5]:
mg.columns = ['Date','Time','Sender','Content1','Content2','Content3','Content4','Content5','Content6','Content7','Content8','Content9','Content10','Content11','Content12','Content13']
In [6]:
mg.Time = mg.Time.apply(lambda x: (x.strip())[0:2])
In [7]:
#mg.head()

Top texters of UpX Team¶

In [8]:
sendr = pd.DataFrame(mg.Sender.value_counts())
sendr.reset_index(inplace=True)
sendr.columns = ['Sender','Count']
#sendr.head(15)
In [9]:
from bokeh.charts import Bar, output_file, show
from bokeh.io import output_notebook
output_notebook()
from bokeh.models import HoverTool
% matplotlib inline

p = Bar(sendr.head(10), label='Sender', values='Count', agg='max',
        title="Number of texts by sender",color = 'Sender',legend=False)

show(p)

Hottest days at UpX Team¶

(Days with high message count)

In [10]:
dat = pd.DataFrame(mg.Date.value_counts())
dat.reset_index(inplace=True)
dat.columns = ['Date','Count']
#dat.head(15)
In [11]:
p = Bar(dat.head(10), label='Date', values='Count', agg='max',
        title="Dates with large message count",color = 'Date',legend=False)

show(p)

tim.reset_index(inplace=True)
tim.columns = ['Time','Count']
#tim.head(15)

show(p)

Top media(image/video/audio) senders of UpX Team¶

In [14]:
media_senders = mg[mg['Content1'] == '<Media omitted>\n']
#media_senders
In [15]:
msendr = pd.DataFrame(media_senders.Sender.value_counts())
msendr.reset_index(inplace=True)
msendr.columns = ['Sender','Count']
#msendr.head(15)
In [16]:
p = Bar(msendr.head(10), label='Sender', values='Count', agg='max',
        title="Number of medias by sender",color = 'Sender',legend=False)

show(p)

Conclusion of above section¶

  • Manav is the top texter of UpX Team followed by Suchit and Nikhil
  • 21st May 2017 was the hottest day of UpX Team followed by 27th May and 19th July
  • 8 pm is the most happening time of UpX Team followed by 10 pm and 1 pm
  • Nikhil is the top media sender of UpX Team followed by Madhu and Suchit

Most frequent words used by Manav¶

In [17]:
manav = mg[mg['Sender'] == 'Manav UpX']
manav = manav[manav['Content1'] != '<Media omitted>\n']
In [18]:
#manav.head()
In [19]:
from wordcloud import WordCloud
cloud = WordCloud(background_color="white",width=800, height=400).generate(' '.join(manav['Content1']))
In [20]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig_size = plt.rcParams["figure.figsize"]
fig_size[0] = 10
fig_size[1] = 5
plt.rcParams["figure.figsize"] = fig_size
plt.imshow(cloud)
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()
